Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:29.32,Ore_Italics,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Large appliances.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:35.59,wantsmost_00:28,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}But what I want most of \Nall is your happiness! \NWow! I'd give myself tons \Nand tons of points for that one!
