Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.81,0:02:20.07,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onii-chan, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.86,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Komachi, don't study under the kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:25.79,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make you sleepy, and if you sleep \Nunder a kotatsu, you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:28.21,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,These things ruin people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:29.80,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it doesn't help when you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:31.25,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,say that as you crawl under the kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.70,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Komachi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:38.84,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What might this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.23,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Just what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:41.93,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:44.85,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Does she seriously want large appliances?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.51,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I know she's my own sister, \Nbut what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.48,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:54.38,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Mom said to order chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:55.20,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.04,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,And cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.02,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:59.60,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I told her I'd do that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.08,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Same thing every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.96,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's that parental instinct thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:05.45,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. Just work hard \Nto get ready for entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:08.37,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, when you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.79,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I couldn't think \Nof another way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.35,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,This is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.24,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It might just piss her off to hear that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.76,Ore_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,from someone who's not working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:20.34,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, at times like that, \Nyou can just say "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.09,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I love you, Komachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:26.36,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel the same, \Nbut thanks, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:27.59,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:33.74,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hikki, are you coming to club today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.19,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.72,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, guess we should get going, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.14,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get my bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.54,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you leave first again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.48,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Like I told you, I'm waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:05.03,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So, um, I might leave early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:08.93,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I might be doing that \Nevery day for a while, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:11.08,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Helping Iroha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.14,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.75,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's plain as day just watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.75,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.82,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.71,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't talk about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.16,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to do this alone again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:31.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only doing it because there's \Nsomething I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.50,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.75,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I will worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.92,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You have bigger things to worry \Nabout than me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:38.79,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:49.39,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Yukinon wanted to \Nbe student council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.27,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:57.34,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I think the whole club \Nshould've accepted that request.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:05:00.65,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's what Yukinon \Nwould've done before all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.11,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:10.59,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I think trying to overcome stuff \Nlike that is what Yukinon likes to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.37,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:16.24,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be a good chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.01,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.75,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, before, it might've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:23.74,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if that's true now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.56,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.97,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yahello!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.93,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:32.93,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:44.68,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I ask something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:49.94,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:52.07,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I leave early \Nevery day for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:56.41,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not as if we're particularly busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.58,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.32,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I've got stuff going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.95,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Komachi's entrance exams, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.09,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:05.55,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That might be better, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:09.52,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much we can do for Komachi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:11.89,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just have to work \Nharder to cover for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.23,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yukinon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.39,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.39,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:24.40,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I should send \NKomachi-chan an email.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.65,comm_center_06:26,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Chiba City Mihama Ward Takasu Community Center
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:28.65,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Isshiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.28,Ore_Main,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.52,Ore_Main,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,She's not with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.32,Ore_Main,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:36.89,Ore_Main,Sec,0000,0000,0000,,I did send her an email...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:40.83,Ore_Main,Sec,0000,0000,0000,,She might still be at her club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.70,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:54.18,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Iroha said she had something \Nto do and left early.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.36,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing a lot of stuff for \Nthe student council, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.77,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You knew about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:01.25,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,She won't say what she's doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.40,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,but I can tell she's really busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:06.80,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You know, if you know \Nthat, you could help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.75,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like she asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:10.40,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one she counts on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:12.87,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,She's just using me because she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.91,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,And you can't refuse, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.52,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's what our club is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.82,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any reason to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And unlike you, I have time on my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:22.20,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:26.56,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:30.66,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You never refuse her either, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.37,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And not because of the club you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:33.50,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:37.95,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the good guy you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.60,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Iroha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.65,comm/library_07:44,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu Community Center\N{\c&H5B85A7&}Mihama Library
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:54.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:58.56,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Did I make you wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:08:00.75,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even wait. I went looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:04.96,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to say "Not \Nat all, I just got here myself"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:10.34,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,It's not heavy today, so I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.15,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:14.33,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. And we're late now, \Nso let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.15,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be focusing on all of \Nyour individual manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:41.85,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Let's figure things out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.91,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Come right out and say \Nwhatever comes to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:47.03,Ore_Main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,We look forward to working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:51.76,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,He calls them here and \Nthen just leaves them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:54.39,Ore_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Should we ask what we're supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.33,Ore_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna ask? I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:57.93,Ore_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have our teacher ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.16,Ore_Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.41,Ore_Main,Rumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.99,Ore_Main,Rumi,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.95,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The girl from Chiba Village in summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:20.13,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,At their camp school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:23.75,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I destroyed the relationships \Namong Tsurumi Rumi's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:27.33,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And I forced Hayama and his \Nbuddies to play bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:29.00,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:30.72,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.13,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:33.90,Ore_Main,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.12,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:36.13,Ore_Main,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.84,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What should we have the kids do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:42.56,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Nothing's been decided yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:46.10,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it'd be best to check with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.91,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Since we agreed to deal with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.90,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,we have to think about it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.90,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.94,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,We should start with something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.08,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,that'll keep them out of the way, \Nbut is still important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:10:00.04,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Like making decorations. \NThey could do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:02.91,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. We'll do that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:07.25,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That'll work for the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.00,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,but if they don't decide what the actual \Nevent will be, this won't last.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.76,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If Isshiki has her reservations \Nwith Tamanawa, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.76,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Got a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:18.70,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.74,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we don't decide \Nwhat the event will be,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:23.01,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,no amount of help will make a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.96,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's all think about it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:28.64,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, you'll never decide anything just \Nsaying vague stuff back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:33.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be best to narrow down what \Nwe'll do, and deliberate on that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:36.74,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't that restrict our outlook?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:40.88,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should all search \Nfor a solution together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:42.49,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But we're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.66,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.06,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all have to consider \Nwhat to do about that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.10,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I understand you feel rushed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:54.34,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,but let's all do our best \Nto cover for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.05,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.16,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:00.71,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But you should really \Nstart that meeting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:03.30,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then let's start the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.43,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've worked together \Non the ground design,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:09.94,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,let's focus more on discussion \Nof the creative end today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:13.31,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,That's very typical of \NChristmas, and of us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:18.44,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A classical Christmas concert seems \Nlike a standard for local events.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.57,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't jazz more Christmasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:28.45,blackboard_11:20,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas Event\N-Orchestra\N-Band\N-Jazz concert\N-Choir\N-Dance\N-Play\N-Gospel\N-Musical\N-Dramatic reading
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.70,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But I think we should take young \Nminds into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:24.78,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.31,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we could get a choir, \Nor even rent a pipe organ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.45,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That's the ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:31.12,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's consider each one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:33.63,blackboard_11:20,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas Event\N-Orchestra\N-Band\N-Jazz concert\N-Choir  -Charades\N-Dance  -Quiz Contest\N-Play  -Bingo\N-Gospel  -Gift Exchange\N-Musical\N-Dramatic reading\N-Christmas Cake
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:35.18,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be faster to pick from \Namong what we've got right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:37.29,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of rejecting anything right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:38.94,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,we need to take all suggestions into account
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:41.38,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and come up with something \Neveryone can agree on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.78,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.86,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Some of these ideas are similar,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.76,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,so it may be possible to combine them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:50.52,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we put all the music ideas \Ntogether into a multi-genre concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:51.90,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That's the ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:53.15,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,From the standpoint of \Nputting ideas together,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.48,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,music and musicals are highly compatible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.80,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That'll work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.82,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we just do it \Nall and make it a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.63,Ore_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So, a musical movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:01.59,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll take the initiative on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:02.91,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That's the ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.66,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Hachiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.84,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Hachiman, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.19,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.80,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,The heat's turned up pretty high in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.36,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.01,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Not right! This is not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.73,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's the heat that's \Nmaking my face red, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:30.85,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That, or it's likely I'm \Ncatching a cold or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.37,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuka is a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:35.52,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Calm down and compose a haiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:39.02,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Me, sick in the head? I am not sick \Nin the head. I'm sick in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:39.02,haiku_12:35,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(730,1)}Me, sick in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:39.02,haiku_12:35,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(651,1)}I am not sick in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.02,haiku_12:35,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(651,1)}I'm sick in the head. (Sick)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.47,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:42.78,Ore_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that fact that I'm composing \Nhaiku is proof I'm sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.74,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.45,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You eat some pretty heavy stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.57,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,I think that kind of food \Nis best when you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:57.89,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,You've seemed that way lately, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:12:58.75,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.20,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:03.93,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.77,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:12.31,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. You don't say \Nstuff like that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:15.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:19.32,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Isshiki asked me for help, \Nso I'm just busy with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:21.32,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the one who pushed \Nher to where she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:22.41,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:24.69,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. So you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:25.77,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.04,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,You really are cool, Hachiman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.29,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean that in a weird way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:37.18,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Like, even if it's tough or painful,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:39.63,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,you work hard on your own, \Nwithout complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.59,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.54,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:46.16,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I complain, and I say spiteful \Nthings all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.59,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.96,Ore_Main,Saika,0000,0000,0000,,But if anything's bothering \Nyou, tell me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:55.71,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:57.62,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cool at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:00.41,Ore_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm just trying to play it cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:05.74,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just being stubborn so \NI won't betray the image
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.12,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,that I've decided I should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:12.03,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But seeing Yuigahama force herself to smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.87,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and the gloomy looks Isshiki gets sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:17.87,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and Tsurumi Rumi standing \Nthere by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:22.71,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And most of all, the quiet smile of \NYukinoshita's that says she's given up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:24.62,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me ask again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.52,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really doing the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.43,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:49.09,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Buying snacks on the way again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:51.70,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,No, it looks like there's no meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.80,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.83,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get to win points with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:01.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need points that \Ncan be won that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:05.25,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Isshiki-chan and Hikigaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.36,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:07.40,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:10.31,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You know Senpai, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:12.26,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we went to the same middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.86,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even you have some friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:18.41,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say we're friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.52,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It's, well... a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.57,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,What "thing"? That's a \Nsuggestive way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:27.20,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, what "thing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:29.49,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.68,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:42.42,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,What? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.17,Ore_Main,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:50.00,Ore_Main,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how I calculate it, \Nwe don't have the budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.09,Ore_Main,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.62,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Either cut out some \Nactivities, or raise funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:56.14,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess all we can do is wait \Nuntil the next meeting to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:16:00.18,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, they're almost finished \Nmaking the decorations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.89,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,What should they do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.69,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How about the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.29,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,We've already got the tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.90,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,but wouldn't it get in the \Nway if we put it up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:12.15,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Negotiate with the center so they'll \Nlet us put it by the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:14.90,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's one week away, \Nso that should be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:17.69,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,We can just carry it to the \Nvenue on the day of the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:19.66,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,That makes sense. Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:23.05,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Doing it this way is very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:25.29,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually giving directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:29.18,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly different \Nfrom just offering support.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.88,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I should talk to him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:35.32,Ore_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can change where this is going \Nand leave the rest to Isshiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:39.31,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There were a lot of ideas, \Nso our side examined them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.90,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Here's what's possible, \Nand what's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.94,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Though, in terms of our budget, \Nmost of them are impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.73,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:48.98,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,This clarifies where we have problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.63,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Now we'll all think about how to solve—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:52.99,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:54.59,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,We only have a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:58.92,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Right... And there are several \Nbands we could outsource.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:00.30,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on how we structure it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:02.50,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can create \Nan event in our own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:05.00,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,So for starters, let's all \Nconsider this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:11.54,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't make a decision at the next \Nmeeting, we can't finish the work in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:12.76,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:13.94,Ore_Main,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:19.88,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. I'm out of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.82,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,She's making decorations?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:31.23,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Making those by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.28,Ore_Main,Rumi,0000,0000,0000,,You can see that much, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:53.42,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How long did you have to delay that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:58.83,Ore_Main,Rumi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:00.18,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You can see that much, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:02.68,Ore_Main,Rumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have anything else to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:04.68,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:06.71,Ore_Main,Rumi,0000,0000,0000,,Bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:07.70,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Lay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:11.15,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm borrowing the cutter, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.89,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, you're not into \Nyounger girls, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.71,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say I have a problem with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:22.95,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.50,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Were you just hitting on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.90,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I like older guys, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.43,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's obviously not what I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:34.51,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to treat me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.59,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the last of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.10,Ore_Main,Rumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.79,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:46.27,Ore_Main,Rumi,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, thank—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.27,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.61,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I think they're still working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.73,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:51.91,Ore_Main,Rumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:04.90,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I know I've saved some people with \Nthe way I used to do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:09.26,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure that alone isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.96,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,My responsibility... The answer I need...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.46,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.11,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.48,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.32,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Were... you shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:40.47,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:43.58,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what brings you out at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.18,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I just had... some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:47.86,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:53.33,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You're helping with Isshiki-san's \Nrequest, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.59,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Well, yeah, as it turned out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:59.57,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't need to lie like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:01.38,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't exactly lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:03.34,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That was one of the reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:06.35,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. It wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:09.00,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I acted on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:10.48,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:13.24,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if I can do anything where
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:15.49,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,your individual actions are concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:17.57,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,nor do I have the right to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:19.46,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.99,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need my permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:26.00,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:31.51,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then was there \Nany need to apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:35.28,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm sure Isshiki-san \Nfeels more comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:36.92,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,working with you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:43.20,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you can solve this on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.50,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You always have before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.85,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not solving anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:51.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm only doing this \Nalone because I am alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.22,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for you, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:55.41,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:58.86,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:02.11,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I only thought I had it all together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:04.77,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,that I understood everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.29,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Yukinoshita...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:12.87,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take a break from the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:17.51,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,If you're only staying out of consideration \Nfor us, it's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:20.67,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not showing consideration or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.63,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You always have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.46,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.22,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:32.20,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't need to push yourself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:36.65,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to break down, \Nthat'd be all there was to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.15,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.18,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to force \Nyourself to attend anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:09.05,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, That Room Continues
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:09.05,Ep_Title - Copy,Title,0000,0000,0000,,to Play Out the Endless Days.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:24:07.84,Next_Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,#08 But Still, Hikigaya Hachiman Is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:42.01,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We should start verifying the \Nagenda of our next meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.01,0:23:44.98,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Agenda! That's totally important!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:47.32,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We can share our schedules \Non the cloud, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:49.46,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud! That sounds totally strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.46,0:23:51.14,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We can upload our resumes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.14,0:23:53.66,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Resume! That sounds delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:54.91,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give ourselves a buffer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:57.17,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Buffer! I totally want one of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.17,0:23:58.95,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Good. I think everything's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.95,0:24:01.94,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's brainstorm \Nand commit to results.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.94,0:24:04.79,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Commit to results! That'll work!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:07.07,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,So, what should we talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.07,0:24:07.84,Ore_Main_Top,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.07,0:24:07.84,Ore_Main_Top,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
